Description.enUS: This is the place to train the infantry, a variety of infantry coordination often can get twice the result

Tooltip.enUS:
You can quickly kill the enemy after opening the skill.
EmpireAntiInfantryInfantryBonzai can be used in a short period of time with the hot light knife to quickly kill enemies at close range.

Role: Assault Infantryman/Anti-light Armor

Special anti tank infantry of the Empire, using plasma cutting cannons, can easily cut through heavily armored zombies and buildings
Role: anti armored infantry

The Empire's advanced flying infantry, using photon missile arrays, can effectively counter air and ground units

can target both air and ground

These young girls who failed to join the ranks of Rocket Angels intend to fight in a more traditional way. Able to use two types of arrows to deal with different situations
Role: range kill/air defense infantry

An excellent assassin master in the Empire, capable of causing fatal damage to lightly armored targets, and using the Smoke Bomb skill can quickly escape crises
Role: Advanced Anti Infantry
Unlock the primary nanotechnology power of the empire, unlock more basic troops to support the empire's battles
Unlock advanced units of the empire, allowing for faster and better expansion of the empire
Unlock the advanced nanotechnology armament power of the empire, allowing it to train and build powerful heavy land and air forces to deal with more powerful enemies
Unlock the experimental weapons of the Empire, release these terrifying killing machines onto the battlefield, and clear all obstacles for the Empire

A powerful superpower with multiple means of destroying the enemy's soul and body, and improving her defensive ability and basic weapon abilities by upgrading infantry attributes
Her power skill needs to be upgraded individually to gain an increase.
Role: Hero

This group of young engineers can use genius-like skills to occupy or repair buildings. After starting to run, they can gain a huge speed increase in a short period of time, but they will be exhausted after a period of time
Role: Capture/repair buildings
